    "body": "The gas cost of this MLOAD is so high because MLOAD will first resize the memory up to the address which you are loading. The overall cost of MLOAD is the constant gas for the op itself plus the cost of the expansion. I know it sounds stupid, but that's what EVM semantics dictate and it's not a bug in go-ethereum.",
